Tandy Corp said February salesand operating revenues were up 12 pct to 244.4 mln dlrs from218.1 mln dlrs a year before.    It said sales and revenues of U.S. retail operations wereup 15 pct to 210.7 mln dlrs from 183.6 mln dlrs a year beforeand sales of U.S. retail stores in existence for more than oneyear were up 13 pct. Reuter&#3;